org.apache.ignite.ml.knn.classification

Class KNNClassificationTrainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.trainers.DatasetTrainer<M,Double>
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.trainers.SingleLabelDatasetTrainer<M>
        • org.apache.ignite.ml.knn.KNNTrainer<KNNClassificationModel,KNNClassificationTrainer>
          • org.apache.ignite.ml.knn.classification.KNNClassificationTrainer

  • public class KNNClassificationTrainer
extends KNNTrainer<KNNClassificationModel,KNNClassificationTrainer>
    KNN classification model trader that trains model on top of distributed spatial indices. Be aware that this model is linked with cluster environment it's been built on and can't be saved or used in other places. Under the hood it keeps Dataset that consists of a set of resources allocated across the cluster.
